### List Transactions [GET /v1/customer/{customerId}/payment-methods/store-credits/transactions{?size,from,sortBy}]

This endpoint returns transactions for all customer store credits.

+ Parameters
    + customerId: 1       (required, number)       - Customer ID.
    + size:   1           (optional, number)       - Page size.
    + from:   1           (optional, number)       - Start element (counting from 0) or # of elements to skip.
    + sortBy: `createdAt` (optional, enum[string]) - Field to sort by (`-fieldName` for descending order).
        + Members
            + `id`
            + `storeCreditId`
            + `orderPaymentId`
            + `debit`
            + `availableBalance`
            + `status`
            + `createdAt`
+ Response 200 (application/json)
